products.description: Have you ever looked down at your cup of coffee only to think, "I wish this wasn't coffee?" Have you ever looked down at your vaporizer and thought "I wish people wouldn't look at me like I'm smoking a robot for a cigarette?" If so, the Vapor Cup may be for you! You may be surprised to learn that the Vapor Cup is not actually a cup at all. It is a fully functional vaporizer for dry herbs that you can inhale from just like a straw in a coffee cup. Just remove the heat sleeve, and you've got precision temperature control! It's super discreet, super fun, and on top of that it's efficient and powerful. Grab the Vapor Cup if you're looking to walk downtown like a person of business while also enjoying a puff of your favorite vapor. Business suit not included.
products.title: Vapor Cup Dry Herb Discrete Vaporizer

products.description: The Arizer Air is as diverse as it is simple. The Arizer Air can vaporize finely ground dry herbs using its three glass stems and five heat settings. Just pull back the silicone cover and insert your materials into the high-quality ceramic heating chamber. When the vaporizer has heated, then you will be able to insert the glass stem of your choice. The Arizer Air can be used for inhalation or aroma therapy, and even comes with some dried flowers for aroma use. If you're looking for a portable vape that can produce high quality vapor, the Arizer Air is a great choice, and will have you relaxed and de-stressed in no time.
products.title: Arizer Air Portable Vaporizer For Dry Herbs
